data.description: Renovated farmhouse, over 8 acres., includes an unfinished tiny house and a huge pole barn.  All this and only 6 miles to Lake Michigan beaches and downtown South Haven.  Home boasts a main floor master with a remodeled master bath and a walk in shower.  Kitchen features quartz countertops with a breakfast bar.  Entertaining is easy with the outdoor living space overlooking rolling countryside.  Nice office/workshop and oversized garage allows for multiple uses.  The pole barn is 32x64 with a concrete floor and electric.  The tiny house is there and ready for you to finish!  This property is perfect for outdoor lovers.
